      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Bubble wrap is the go-to protective material for glassware, ceramics, and delicate items across Malaysia. But not all bubble wrap is created equal. Choosing the right thickness, applying proper technique, and sourcing quality wholesale bubble wrap can mean the difference between zero breakage and disappointed customers.</p>
