        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">Can I use recycled/secondhand bubble wrap?</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed">Not recommended. Used bubble wrap has lost air in many pockets, reducing cushioning effectiveness. Always use fresh bubble wrap for valuable items.</p>
